      <title>Movie Geek&#39;s Way To Learn The ABCs</title>
      <link>http://chosancarson.github.io/geekygearblog/2016/06/11/movie-geeks-way-to-learn-the-abcs</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jun 2016 13:28:23 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://chosancarson.github.io/geekygearblog/2016/06/11/movie-geeks-way-to-learn-the-abcs</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;The guys over at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXZQA0vdUY4ZRzEZ5TFKdNA&#34;&gt;Burger Fiction&lt;/a&gt; have put together an entertaining supercut of movies to teach the ABCs. I tested this with my two year old and he seemed to enjoy it. Then around letter L he fell asleep. Sweet! This video is a win-win. I get to play an educational video for my little one that I also enjoy watching, and I get peace and quiet afterwards.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;iframe width=&#34;560&#34; height=&#34;315&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/_Dzq6sImlCc&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;some-other-shows-my-son-loves:c37b3216f9b8f6a7ce5a0179d7c6d348&#34;&gt;Some other shows my son loves&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/gp/search/ref=as_li_qf_sp_sr_il?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=geekygearblog-20&amp;keywords=ABC Galaxy - Season 1&amp;index=aps&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=ada44600da275b42834634dc108ac397&#34;&gt;&lt;img border=&#34;0&#34; src=&#34;//ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ASIN=B016CEO8QY&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;WS=1&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;tag=geekygearblog-20&#34; &gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=geekygearblog-20&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=1&amp;camp=1789&#34; width=&#34;1&#34; height=&#34;1&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;border:none !important; margin:0px !important;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://amzn.to/1PTezCy&#34;&gt;ABC Galaxy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
It&amp;rsquo;s a really simple show about Giggs &amp;amp; Hugg. They are two friends that travel around and explore the &amp;ldquo;ABC Galaxy&amp;rdquo; in their junky  spaceship. Little Ezekiel loves it and is slowly learning his abc&amp;rsquo;s. It&amp;rsquo;s adorable to watch him pronounce his letters along with the show.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003ITZBV8/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003ITZBV8&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=geekygearblog-20&amp;linkId=a2cbac0f84a34b920a5b2644b0081e8a&#34;&gt;&lt;img border=&#34;0&#34; src=&#34;//ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ASIN=B003ITZBV8&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;WS=1&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;tag=geekygearblog-20&#34; &gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=geekygearblog-20&amp;l=am2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003ITZBV8&#34; width=&#34;1&#34; height=&#34;1&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;border:none !important; margin:0px !important;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://amzn.to/1tjSNgY&#34;&gt;Sesame Street: Preschool is Cool: ABCs with Elmo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
You can&amp;rsquo;t really go wrong with sesame street. I play this one for Zeke every couple of days, he likes all the songs. I&amp;rsquo;ve noticed for a DVD titled &amp;ldquo;ABCs with Elmo&amp;rdquo; it&amp;rsquo;s a little light on actual Elmo. It seems like he just pops in to introduce songs. Then again I haven&amp;rsquo;t sat down and really watched it just an observation from afar.&lt;/p&gt;
